Here are some commonly used Markdown shortcuts for formatting text:

### **Text Formatting**
| Format            | Markdown Syntax           | Example                     | Result                 |
|--------------------|---------------------------|-----------------------------|------------------------|
| Bold              | `**text**` or `__text__` | **`**Bold**`**             | **Bold**              |
| Italics           | `*text*` or `_text_`     | *`*Italic*`*               | *Italic*              |
| Strikethrough     | `~~text~~`               | `~~Strikethrough~~`        | ~~Strikethrough~~     |

---

### **Headings**
| Heading Level | Markdown Syntax  | Example                | Result               |
|---------------|------------------|------------------------|----------------------|
| H1            | `# text`         | `# Heading 1`         | # Heading 1          |
| H2            | `## text`        | `## Heading 2`        | ## Heading 2         |
| H3            | `### text`       | `### Heading 3`       | ### Heading 3        |

*(Add more `#` for deeper headings up to H6.)*

---

### **Lists**
| Type       | Markdown Syntax                      | Example                              | Result                            |
|------------|--------------------------------------|--------------------------------------|-----------------------------------|
| Unordered  | `-` or `*` or `+`                   | `- Item` or `* Item`                | - Item                           |
| Ordered    | `1.`, `2.`, etc.                    | `1. First Item`                     | 1. First Item                    |
| Sub-list   | Indent with 2 spaces under parent   | `- Parent`<br> `  - Child`          | - Parent<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;- Child |

---

### **Links and Images**
| Type        | Markdown Syntax                                      | Example                                            | Result                          |
|-------------|------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------|
| Hyperlink   | `[text](URL)`                                       | `[OpenAI](https://openai.com)`                   | [OpenAI](https://openai.com)   |
| Image       | `![alt text](image URL)`                            | `![Logo](https://openai.com/logo.png)`           | ![Logo](https://openai.com/logo.png) |

---

### **Code**
| Type           | Markdown Syntax           | Example                       | Result                    |
|-----------------|---------------------------|-------------------------------|---------------------------|
| Inline Code     | `` `code` ``             | `` `print("Hello")` ``        | `print("Hello")`          |
| Code Block      | ```` ```language ``` ```` | ```` ```python\nprint() ``` `` | ```python
print() ``` |

---

### **Blockquotes**
| Markdown Syntax      | Example            | Result                 |
|-----------------------|--------------------|------------------------|
| `> text`             | `> Blockquote`    | > Blockquote          |

---

### **Horizontal Line**
| Markdown Syntax | Result       |
|------------------|--------------|
| `---` or `***`   | Horizontal Line |

---

